  <span id="freeText14344888658666124358" style="display:none">Written in a deeply moralistic omnipotent 3rd person voice that can only be Coelho's this suspense-filled tale of obsession is a departure from Coelho's usual works in that it is written in the Roman Noir tradition. This is a gripping, page-turning thriller. <br /><br />Are you ready? Because there is a serial killer stalking Cannes.</span>
