        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer67615723" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17901004701466920424">I wish if I had read a review on Paulo Coelho&apos;s book The Winner Stands Alone!!!Then I wouldn’t waste money for it.<br/>I have read almost all of Paulo Coelho&apos;s books. I have them all in my library but this one is the worst book of Paulo. It gave me so dark feelings…it seems like he is describing Cannes festival but I don’t have any idea about how truth is it. I wonder why he wanted to write on this subject???<br/>Yes it is different but with a lack of wisdom, it’s poorly written. I’ll forget this book of </span>
  <span id="freeText17901004701466920424" style="display:none">I wish if I had read a review on Paulo Coelho's book The Winner Stands Alone!!!Then I wouldn’t waste money for it.<br />I have read almost all of Paulo Coelho's books. I have them all in my library but this one is the worst book of Paulo. It gave me so dark feelings…it seems like he is describing Cannes festival but I don’t have any idea about how truth is it. I wonder why he wanted to write on this subject???<br />Yes it is different but with a lack of wisdom, it’s poorly written. I’ll forget this book of Coelho, so that I can read his future books<br /></span>
